Global RTD Canned Cocktails Market

The RTD canned cocktails market is expected to witness market growth at a rate of 20.00% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028 and is expected to reach USD 2.79 billion by 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on RTD canned cocktails market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecast period while providing their impacts on the marketâ€™s growth. The increase in the consumption of alcoholic beverages is escalating the growth of RTD canned cocktails market.

RTD alcoholic beverages refer to the ready-to-drink beverages containing certain amount of alcohol content in them. These products are available in the prepared form that is ready for consumption. Numerous RTD alcoholic beverages are available and these are served for various purposes.

The rise in the demand for low content alcohol-based flavored drinks owning to the increasing health concerns, acts as one of the major factors driving the RTD canned cocktails market. The wide availability of variety of ready to drink (RTD) cocktails that are infused with numerous flavors such as lavender, ginger and rose and increase in demand for pre-mix cocktails due to busy lifestyles accelerate the market growth. The increase premiumization of the product with enhanced taste, quality, package design and flavors to meet the changing preferences of the consumers and rapid shift to RTD cocktails as a substitute for wine and spirits further influence the market. Additionally, growth of e-commerce sector, increase in awareness regarding low content alcohol, surge in disposable income of people and increase in the online sales positively affect the RTD canned cocktails market. Furthermore, convenient package design extends profitable opportunities to the market players in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

On the other hand, heavy duties and taxation and health issues related to consumption of alcohol are the factors expected to obstruct the market growth. Cultural and religious beliefs across various regions are projected to challenge the RTD canned cocktails market in the forecast period of 2021-2028.

